select REP_SEVERITY_TYPES.SEVERITY as Number, trim(REP_SEVERITY_TYPES.NAME) as Name from [Reporter].REP_SEVERITY_TYPES REP_SEVERITY_TYPES

with REP_AUDIT_ACK3 as (select REP_AUDIT_ACK.STARTDATE as STARTDATE, REP_AUDIT_ACK.ENDDATE as ENDDATE from [Reporter].REP_AUDIT_ACK REP_AUDIT_ACK where (REP_AUDIT_ACK."STATE" = 1) ) select (REP_AUDIT_ACK3.ENDDATE - REP_AUDIT_ACK3.STARTDATE) as Duration from REP_AUDIT_ACK3
